---
// Founders section — Tre + Nicolas
---

<section id="about" class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-foggy-bg">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 md:px-8">
    <h2 class="font-bold tracking-tight text-foggy-ink" style="font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 44px);">
      Built by people who've been inside the problem.
    </h2>

    <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <!-- Tre -->
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8">
        <h3 class="text-[20px] font-bold text-foggy-ink">Tre Mansdoerfer</h3>
        <p class="mt-1 text-[14px] text-foggy-ink-light">CEO</p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-[17px] leading-[1.6] text-foggy-ink">
          Tre spent four years at Microsoft on the Azure edge compute and CDN team, where he supported the strategy and execution for edge sites in markets where full hyperscale campuses didn't pencil out. That work showed him why hyperscalers cannot serve emerging markets the way they serve California — a dollar of capital deployed in the US generates 10-20× the return of a dollar deployed in Lagos or Nairobi. Even when leadership wanted to invest, the math pushed Microsoft elsewhere. Foggy is the company he wished existed when he was watching that decision get made.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-[14px] text-foggy-ink-light">HBS MBA '26.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Nicolas -->
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8">
        <h3 class="text-[20px] font-bold text-foggy-ink">Nicolas</h3>
        <p class="mt-1 text-[14px] text-foggy-ink-light">CTO</p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-[17px] leading-[1.6] text-foggy-ink">
          Nicolas leads engineering. He wraps up his MS coursework through Harvard's MS/MBA program in May 2026, then joins Foggy full-time. He's writing the next generation of the orchestration layer that pools idle compute inside customer institutions into a usable inference fleet — the part that has to scale from a single laptop in a Nairobi bank to thousands of nodes across the continent.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-[14px] text-foggy-ink-light">Harvard MS/MBA '26.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="mt-8 text-center text-[15px] italic text-foggy-ink-light">
      Met at HBS in 2024. Building Foggy together since.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
